properties.description: Uses SF flight blob file with Pax and Mission ID as source. Adds flight category. Creates temp flight number as integer for join to flt nbr range.

transformations.name: AddWrkflwIDandTS
transformations.description: Adds ADF run ID and timestamp

transformations.name: FLTTYPEfilter
transformations.description: Filters out offline flights

transformations.name: ActualAirportIDifNULL
transformations.description: If actual depart/arrive airport ID is null, populates with sched depart/arrive airport ID.

transformations.name: SchdDepAirportLookup
transformations.description: Looks up IATA, ICAO and FAA airport codes for scheduled departure airport.

transformations.name: UpdateSchdDepAirportCode
transformations.description: Populates sched departure airport code with IATA, ICAO or FAA code (whichever is available first).

transformations.name: RemoveSchdDepAirportCols
transformations.description: Removes unneeded lookup columns inserted from airport reference table.

transformations.name: SchdArrAirportLookup
transformations.description: Looks up IATA, ICAO and FAA airport codes for scheduled arrival airport.

transformations.name: UpdateSchdArrAirportCode
transformations.description: Populates sched arrival airport code with IATA, ICAO or FAA code (whichever is available first).

transformations.name: RemoveSchArrAirportCols
transformations.description: Removes unneeded lookup columns inserted from airport reference table.

transformations.name: ActDepAirportLookup
transformations.description: Looks up IATA, ICAO and FAA airport codes for actual departure airport.

transformations.name: UpdateActDepAirportCode
transformations.description: Populates actual departure airport code with IATA, ICAO or FAA code (whichever is available first).

transformations.name: RemoveActDepAirportCols
transformations.description: Removes unneeded lookup columns inserted from airport reference table.

transformations.name: ActArrAirportLookup
transformations.description: Looks up IATA, ICAO and FAA airport codes for actual arrival airport.

transformations.name: UpdateActArrAirportCode
transformations.description: Populates actual arrival airport code with IATA, ICAO or FAA code (whichever is available first).

transformations.name: RemoveActArrAirportCols
transformations.description: Removes unneeded lookup columns inserted from airport reference table. Changes "pax" column to "SF_Pax"

transformations.name: ConditionalSplit1
transformations.description: Splits flight data into two sets: one with flight numbers beginning with "CMB" and another for purely numeric flight numbers.

transformations.name: ChangeFltNumToINT
transformations.description: Adds temp "flight_number_INT" field to convert flight_number value to integer for join to flt number range matrix (keeping "flight_number" as string).

transformations.name: RenameFlightType
transformations.description: Renames "flight_type" to "flt_type" to avoid duplicate column names with "FLIGHT_TYPE" in FltNbrRangeMatrix.

transformations.name: ChangeBegEndFltNbrToInt
transformations.description: Converts "BEGIN_FLT_NBR," "END_FLT_NBR" to integer for use in join.

transformations.name: JoinToFltNbrRangeMatrix
transformations.description: Joins flight data to flight number matrix on flt number and sked dep date to get flight type and subtype.

transformations.name: CMBfltnbrRevCat
transformations.description: Assigns "DOD Int'l" revenue type to all flight numbers beginning with "CMB."

transformations.name: STDfltnbrRevCat
transformations.description: Changes flight data "flt_type" to "flight_type" and flt number range data "FLIGHT_TYPE" to "REVENUE_TYPE" and "FLIGHT_SUBTYPE" to "REVENUE_SUBTYPE". Drops EFF and END dates, BEGIN and END flt number fields from Flight Number Matrix. "flight_number_INT" field dropped.

transformations.name: UnionCMBandSTDfltnmbrs
transformations.description: Combining rows from transformation 'CMBfltnbrRevCat, and STDfltnbrRevCat'

transformations.name: ChangeDateTimefieldstoTimestamp
transformations.description: Change date/time fields for OOOI, scheduled, estimated arr and dep times from string to timestamp to aid in SQL datatype determination.

typeProperties.script:
parameters{
	run_id as string
}
source(output(
		flight_id as integer,
		flight_number as string,
		flight_date as string,
		aircraft_registration_number as string,
		aircraft_type as string,
		ops_type as string,
		scheduled_departure as string,
		scheduled_arrival as string,
		estimated_departure as string,
		estimated_arrival as string,
		actual_oooi_out as string,
		actual_oooi_off as string,
		actual_oooi_on as string,
		actual_oooi_in as string,
		base_airport_id as string,
		sched_depart_airport_id as string,
		sched_arrive_airport_id as string,
		actual_depart_airport_id as string,
		actual_arrive_airport_id as string,
		base_airport as string,
		scheduled_departure_airport as string,
		scheduled_arrival_airport as string,
		actual_departure_airport as string,
		actual_arrival_airport as string,
		is_verified as boolean,
		notes as string,
		is_canceled as boolean,
		flight_type as string,
		cargo_weight as integer,
		cargo_on as integer,
		cargo_off as integer,
		fuel_out as double,
		fuel_in as double,
		fuel_uplift as integer,
		fuel_uplifts as string,
		maint_log_page as string,
		lndg_touchdown_zone as string,
		lndg_midfield as string,
		lndg_rollout as string,
		lndg_actual_braking as string,
		pax as integer,
		mission_id as string,
		updated_at as string,
		customer_name as string,
		customer_code as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	documentForm: 'documentPerLine',
	dateFormats: ['yyyy-MM-dd'],
	timestampFormats: ['yyyy-MM-dd\'T\'HH:mm:ss'],
	preferredIntegralType: 'integer',
	preferredFractionalType: 'decimal') ~> SFFlight
source(output(
		airport_id as string,
		iata_code as string,
		icao_code as string,
		faa_code as string,
		airport_name as string,
		city_name as string,
		state_code as string,
		country_code as string,
		weather_zone as string,
		latitude as string,
		longitude as string,
		elevation_feet as string,
		iana_timezone as string,
		is_base as boolean,
		base_initial as string,
		is_active as boolean,
		is_deleted as boolean
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	documentForm: 'documentPerLine') ~> AirportReferenceJSON
source(output(
		EFF_DATE as string,
		END_DATE as string,
		BEGIN_FLT_NBR as string,
		END_FLT_NBR as string,
		FLIGHT_TYPE as string,
		FLIGHT_SUBTYPE as string,
		FLT_TYPE_OPS_REPORT as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> FltNbrRangeMatrixCSV
SFFlight derive(ADF_TIMESTAMP = currentTimestamp(),
		RUN_ID = $run_id) ~> AddWrkflwIDandTS
AddWrkflwIDandTS filter(flight_type <=> 'flight' || flight_type <=> 'continuation' || flight_type <=> 'divert' || flight_type <=> 'return' || flight_type <=> 'taxi-back') ~> FLTTYPEfilter
FLTTYPEfilter derive(actual_arrive_airport_id = iif(isNull(actual_arrive_airport_id), sched_arrive_airport_id, actual_arrive_airport_id),
		actual_depart_airport_id = iif(isNull(actual_depart_airport_id) , sched_depart_airport_id, actual_depart_airport_id)) ~> ActualAirportIDifNULL
AirportReferenceJSON select(mapColumn(
		airport_id,
		iata_code,
		icao_code,
		faa_code
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> PareAirportReference
ActualAirportIDifNULL, PareAirportReference lookup(sched_depart_airport_id == airport_id,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> SchdDepAirportLookup
SchdDepAirportLookup derive(scheduled_departure_airport = coalesce(iata_code,icao_code,faa_code)) ~> UpdateSchdDepAirportCode
UpdateSchdDepAirportCode select(mapColumn(
		flight_id,
		flight_number,
		flight_date,
		aircraft_registration_number,
		aircraft_type,
		ops_type,
		scheduled_departure,
		scheduled_arrival,
		estimated_departure,
		estimated_arrival,
		actual_oooi_out,
		actual_oooi_off,
		actual_oooi_on,
		actual_oooi_in,
		base_airport_id,
		sched_depart_airport_id,
		sched_arrive_airport_id,
		actual_depart_airport_id,
		actual_arrive_airport_id,
		base_airport,
		scheduled_departure_airport,
		scheduled_arrival_airport,
		actual_departure_airport,
		actual_arrival_airport,
		is_verified,
		notes,
		is_canceled,
		flight_type,
		cargo_weight,
		cargo_on,
		cargo_off,
		fuel_out,
		fuel_in,
		fuel_uplift,
		fuel_uplifts,
		maint_log_page,
		lndg_touchdown_zone,
		lndg_midfield,
		lndg_rollout,
		lndg_actual_braking,
		pax,
		mission_id,
		updated_at,
		ADF_TIMESTAMP,
		RUN_ID
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RemoveSchdDepAirportCols
RemoveSchdDepAirportCols, PareAirportReference lookup(sched_arrive_airport_id == airport_id,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> SchdArrAirportLookup
SchdArrAirportLookup derive(scheduled_arrival_airport = coalesce(iata_code,icao_code,faa_code)) ~> UpdateSchdArrAirportCode
UpdateSchdArrAirportCode select(mapColumn(
		flight_id,
		flight_number,
		flight_date,
		aircraft_registration_number,
		aircraft_type,
		ops_type,
		scheduled_departure,
		scheduled_arrival,
		estimated_departure,
		estimated_arrival,
		actual_oooi_out,
		actual_oooi_off,
		actual_oooi_on,
		actual_oooi_in,
		base_airport_id,
		sched_depart_airport_id,
		sched_arrive_airport_id,
		actual_depart_airport_id,
		actual_arrive_airport_id,
		base_airport,
		scheduled_departure_airport,
		scheduled_arrival_airport,
		actual_departure_airport,
		actual_arrival_airport,
		is_verified,
		notes,
		is_canceled,
		flight_type,
		cargo_weight,
		cargo_on,
		cargo_off,
		fuel_out,
		fuel_in,
		fuel_uplift,
		fuel_uplifts,
		maint_log_page,
		lndg_touchdown_zone,
		lndg_midfield,
		lndg_rollout,
		lndg_actual_braking,
		pax,
		mission_id,
		updated_at,
		ADF_TIMESTAMP,
		RUN_ID
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RemoveSchArrAirportCols
RemoveSchArrAirportCols, PareAirportReference lookup(actual_depart_airport_id == airport_id,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> ActDepAirportLookup
ActDepAirportLookup derive(actual_departure_airport = coalesce(iata_code,icao_code,faa_code)) ~> UpdateActDepAirportCode
UpdateActDepAirportCode select(mapColumn(
		flight_id,
		flight_number,
		flight_date,
		aircraft_registration_number,
		aircraft_type,
		ops_type,
		scheduled_departure,
		scheduled_arrival,
		estimated_departure,
		estimated_arrival,
		actual_oooi_out,
		actual_oooi_off,
		actual_oooi_on,
		actual_oooi_in,
		base_airport_id,
		sched_depart_airport_id,
		sched_arrive_airport_id,
		actual_depart_airport_id,
		actual_arrive_airport_id,
		base_airport,
		scheduled_departure_airport,
		scheduled_arrival_airport,
		actual_departure_airport,
		actual_arrival_airport,
		is_verified,
		notes,
		is_canceled,
		flight_type,
		cargo_weight,
		cargo_on,
		cargo_off,
		fuel_out,
		fuel_in,
		fuel_uplift,
		fuel_uplifts,
		maint_log_page,
		lndg_touchdown_zone,
		lndg_midfield,
		lndg_rollout,
		lndg_actual_braking,
		pax,
		mission_id,
		updated_at,
		ADF_TIMESTAMP,
		RUN_ID
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RemoveActDepAirportCols
RemoveActDepAirportCols, PareAirportReference lookup(actual_arrive_airport_id == airport_id,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> ActArrAirportLookup
ActArrAirportLookup derive(actual_arrival_airport = coalesce(iata_code,icao_code,faa_code)) ~> UpdateActArrAirportCode
UpdateActArrAirportCode select(mapColumn(
		flight_id,
		flight_number,
		flight_date,
		aircraft_registration_number,
		aircraft_type,
		ops_type,
		scheduled_departure_airport,
		scheduled_arrival_airport,
		scheduled_departure,
		scheduled_arrival,
		actual_oooi_out,
		actual_oooi_off,
		actual_oooi_on,
		actual_oooi_in,
		estimated_arrival,
		estimated_departure,
		base_airport_id,
		sched_depart_airport_id,
		sched_arrive_airport_id,
		actual_depart_airport_id,
		actual_arrive_airport_id,
		base_airport,
		actual_departure_airport,
		actual_arrival_airport,
		is_verified,
		notes,
		is_canceled,
		flight_type,
		cargo_weight,
		cargo_on,
		cargo_off,
		fuel_out,
		fuel_in,
		fuel_uplift,
		fuel_uplifts,
		maint_log_page,
		lndg_touchdown_zone,
		lndg_midfield,
		lndg_rollout,
		lndg_actual_braking,
		SF_pax = pax,
		mission_id,
		updated_at,
		ADF_TIMESTAMP,
		RUN_ID
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RemoveActArrAirportCols
RemoveActArrAirportCols split(startsWith(flight_number,'CMB'),
	disjoint: false) ~> ConditionalSplit1@(CMBfltnbr, STDfltnbr)
ConditionalSplit1@STDfltnbr derive(flight_number_INT = toInteger(flight_number)) ~> ChangeFltNumToINT
ChangeFltNumToINT select(mapColumn(
		flight_id,
		flight_number,
		flight_date,
		aircraft_registration_number,
		aircraft_type,
		ops_type,
		scheduled_departure_airport,
		scheduled_arrival_airport,
		scheduled_departure,
		scheduled_arrival,
		actual_oooi_out,
		actual_oooi_off,
		actual_oooi_on,
		actual_oooi_in,
		estimated_arrival,
		estimated_departure,
		base_airport_id,
		sched_depart_airport_id,
		sched_arrive_airport_id,
		actual_depart_airport_id,
		actual_arrive_airport_id,
		base_airport,
		actual_departure_airport,
		actual_arrival_airport,
		is_verified,
		notes,
		is_canceled,
		flt_type = flight_type,
		cargo_weight,
		cargo_on,
		cargo_off,
		fuel_out,
		fuel_in,
		fuel_uplift,
		fuel_uplifts,
		maint_log_page,
		lndg_touchdown_zone,
		lndg_midfield,
		lndg_rollout,
		lndg_actual_braking,
		SF_pax,
		mission_id,
		updated_at,
		ADF_TIMESTAMP,
		RUN_ID,
		flight_number_INT
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RenameFlightType
FltNbrRangeMatrixCSV derive(BEGIN_FLT_NBR = toInteger(BEGIN_FLT_NBR),
		END_FLT_NBR = toInteger(END_FLT_NBR)) ~> ChangeBegEndFltNbrToInt
RenameFlightType, ChangeBegEndFltNbrToInt join(flight_number_INT >= BEGIN_FLT_NBR
	&& flight_number_INT <= END_FLT_NBR
	&& scheduled_departure >= EFF_DATE
	&& scheduled_departure <= END_DATE,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'right')~> JoinToFltNbrRangeMatrix
ConditionalSplit1@CMBfltnbr derive(REVENUE_TYPE = "DOD Int'l",
		REVENUE_SUBTYPE = "International",
		FLT_TYPE_OPS_REPORT = "DOD Int'l") ~> CMBfltnbrRevCat
JoinToFltNbrRangeMatrix select(mapColumn(
		flight_id,
		flight_number,
		flight_date,
		aircraft_registration_number,
		aircraft_type,
		ops_type,
		scheduled_departure_airport,
		scheduled_arrival_airport,
		scheduled_departure,
		scheduled_arrival,
		actual_oooi_out,
		actual_oooi_off,
		actual_oooi_on,
		actual_oooi_in,
		estimated_arrival,
		estimated_departure,
		base_airport_id,
		sched_depart_airport_id,
		sched_arrive_airport_id,
		actual_depart_airport_id,
		actual_arrive_airport_id,
		base_airport,
		actual_departure_airport,
		actual_arrival_airport,
		is_verified,
		notes,
		is_canceled,
		flight_type = flt_type,
		cargo_weight,
		cargo_on,
		cargo_off,
		fuel_out,
		fuel_in,
		fuel_uplift,
		fuel_uplifts,
		maint_log_page,
		lndg_touchdown_zone,
		lndg_midfield,
		lndg_rollout,
		lndg_actual_braking,
		SF_pax,
		mission_id,
		updated_at,
		ADF_TIMESTAMP,
		RUN_ID,
		REVENUE_TYPE = FLIGHT_TYPE,
		REVENUE_SUBTYPE = FLIGHT_SUBTYPE,
		FLT_TYPE_OPS_REPORT
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> STDfltnbrRevCat
CMBfltnbrRevCat, STDfltnbrRevCat union(byName: true)~> UnionCMBandSTDfltnmbrs
UnionCMBandSTDfltnmbrs derive(scheduled_departure = toTimestamp(scheduled_departure,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'),
		scheduled_arrival = toTimestamp(scheduled_arrival,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'),
		actual_oooi_out = toTimestamp(actual_oooi_out,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'),
		actual_oooi_off = toTimestamp(actual_oooi_off,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'),
		actual_oooi_on = toTimestamp(actual_oooi_on,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'),
		actual_oooi_in = toTimestamp(actual_oooi_in,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'),
		estimated_arrival = toTimestamp(estimated_arrival,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'),
		estimated_departure = toTimestamp(estimated_departure,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'),
		updated_at = toTimestamp(updated_at,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')) ~> ChangeDateTimefieldstoTimestamp
ChangeDateTimefieldstoTimestamp sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	input(
		actual_arrival_airport as string,
		actual_arrive_airport_id as string,
		actual_depart_airport_id as string,
		actual_departure_airport as string,
		actual_oooi_in as timestamp,
		actual_oooi_off as timestamp,
		actual_oooi_on as timestamp,
		actual_oooi_out as timestamp,
		aircraft_registration_number as string,
		aircraft_type as string,
		base_airport as string,
		base_airport_id as string,
		cargo_off as integer,
		cargo_on as integer,
		cargo_weight as integer,
		estimated_arrival as timestamp,
		estimated_departure as timestamp,
		flight_date as date,
		flight_id as integer,
		flight_number as string,
		flight_type as string,
		fuel_in as double,
		fuel_out as double,
		fuel_uplift as integer,
		fuel_uplifts as string,
		is_canceled as string,
		is_verified as string,
		lndg_actual_braking as string,
		lndg_midfield as string,
		lndg_rollout as string,
		lndg_touchdown_zone as string,
		maint_log_page as string,
		notes as string,
		ops_type as string,
		sched_arrive_airport_id as string,
		sched_depart_airport_id as string,
		scheduled_arrival as timestamp,
		scheduled_arrival_airport as string,
		scheduled_departure as timestamp,
		scheduled_departure_airport as string,
		updated_at as timestamp,
		ADF_TIMESTAMP as timestamp,
		RUN_ID as string
	),
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	recreate:true,
	format: 'table',
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	errorHandlingOption: 'stopOnFirstError') ~> FlightToSQL
